[00:06] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'You probably weren\'t expecting me to sound like this. But that\'s the beautiful thing about innovation. You think you\'ve heard it all before. Every cliffhanger and every twist.'

[00:18] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Every revolution to how you work. But then it hits you suddenly. Like an uncontrollable urge to sing. &gt;&gt; [music]'

[00:33] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: '&gt;&gt; You know the vibes out on this side. Yeah. You know the vibes. Been in this thing winning rings for a while. And when you can\'t seem to find the words, get creative. &gt;&gt; [crying and screaming]'

[00:51] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: '&gt;&gt; Well, I really just wanted to give you something to get you hooked. Because sometimes it\'s not what you say, [music] but how you say it.'
